short.zh_CN: 这是 MarkLib 浏览器扩展

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The MarkLib browser extension is your essential tool for seamless bookmark management and knowledge transformation. With just a click, effortlessly save web pages to your MarkLib account, capturing full-text content and metadata. This extension not only organizes your bookmarks but also integrates them into a powerful knowledge base, enabling AI-driven search and insights. Install the MarkLib extension today to enhance your productivity, ensure easy access to your curated content, and transform your browsing experience into a smart, efficient knowledge journey.
